<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">{!Contact.Title} {!Contact.FirstName}&nbsp;{!Contact.LastName}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">{!Contact.MailingAddress}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">{!Today}</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText"><span style="font-size: 13.3333px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Student ID Number:&nbsp;{!Contact.LSTM_No__c}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Course:&nbsp;&nbsp;{!Student_Programme__c.Programme__c}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Thank you for applying for a place on {!Student_Programme__c.Programme__c}.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">I am please to inform you that your application has been approved and is conditional on receipt of the course fee which must be paid by 13th December.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">LSTM have partnered with Flywire to provide you with an easy and secure method of sending fee payments in your home currency. You can pay by bank transfer, debit/credit card and e-wallet methods.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">How to pay:&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">1. Visit&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">lstmed.flywire.com&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">and choose your country&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">2. Input the amount you are paying in GBP&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Payment by bank transfer or international debit/credit card = {!Student_Programme__c.Invoice_Amount__c}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Payment by domestic UK credit/debit cards in GBP = {!Student_Programme__c.UK_Card_Payment_Fee__c}&nbsp;(incl. 2% fee)&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">3. Choose your payment method and make your payment to Flywire&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">4. Enter your details and if you are paying on behalf of a student, the details of the student you are paying for&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">5. Track and confirm your payment by email, SMS, or by logging into lstmed.flywire.com&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Registration will open a week before the official start date of the course when you will receive a further e-mail from us containing details of how to access the virtual learning environment (“BrightSpace”).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Please do contact us with any questions in the meantime.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Best wishes<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;{!User.LastName}<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Administrator – Academic Registry<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Email: MyLSTM@lstmed.ac.uk<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Telephone:&nbsp;{!User.Phone}&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoPlainText" style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></p>]]></td>
</tr>
